{"tid":818194,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"英倫扮工室IX","createTime":"2018-09-14T02:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T11:54:20.000Z","uid":136588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4db40d25b7f03d5e39e5eb3884839b7964e4d974","tid":818194,"uid":136588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:52:07.000Z","msg":"The first step to UK is to read through all the information provided (google it yourself if necessary)<br />\nas some British might not even know how to do their job (HR are all the same around the globe)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Visa</span><br />\n<br />\nTier 5 (Youth Mobility Scheme) visa - Also known as working holiday<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/tier-5-youth-mobility\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Ftier-5-youth-mobility&d=AAikRAnnkpmqLFbgyV%2BMLMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b283aaa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/tier-5-youth-mobility</a><br />\n<br />\nDon't worry about below if you are using BNO<br />\n<ins>Note: If you&rsquo;re applying this visa using HKSAR passport<br />\nYou need to be sponsored<br />\nThere will be an annual quota</ins><br />\n<br />\nTier 2 (General) visa<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/tier-2-general\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Ftier-2-general&d=AAikRAnnkpmqLFbgyV%2BMLMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c341f2ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/tier-2-general</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<del>this shit is such a long and painful process, especially if your employer is not familiar to this visa<br />\n</del><br />\nYou can apply for a Tier 2 (General) visa if:<br />\nyou&rsquo;ve been <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">OFFERED</span> a skilled job in the UK<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Apply to settle</span><br />\n<br />\nIf you truly love your life in UK<br />\nyou might apply to settle<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Option 1</span><br />\n<br />\nIf you have been living in UK for 10 years<br />\nand met certain requirements<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/long-residence/eligibility\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Flong-residence%2Feligibility&d=AAikRAnnkpmqLFbgyV%2BMLMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=d2a92969\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/long-residence/eligibility</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Option 2</span><br />\nIf you have been living and working (under Tier 2) in the UK for 5 years<br />\nand met certain requirements<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/settle-in-the-uk/y/you-have-a-work-visa/tier-2-general-visa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fsettle-in-the-uk%2Fy%2Fyou-have-a-work-visa%2Ftier-2-general-visa&d=AAikRAnnkpmqLFbgyV%2BMLMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2f667291\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/settle-in-the-uk/y/you-have-a-work-visa/tier-2-general-visa</a>"},{"pid":"927bd31e75cc2cd325e2ec77453c87dd6695b85f","tid":818194,"uid":136588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"又星期五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b395281b847278b589782379bdf24377f0d1bb0c","tid":818194,"uid":86517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T11:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d447cc779ac5fddb35707e765e772c5ffdd9d61b","tid":818194,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T06:37:28.000Z","msg":"Colchester - working holiday 求救 <br />\n有咩工可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd20a6d385e6667613972f8172fb0a2c43cd931","tid":8